The texts on this cover are just placeholders, added by the book cover designer. You can customize them instantly by clicking CUSTOMIZE.

This book cover has 3 lines for the title, 1 line for the subtitle, 2 lines for the author, 2 lines for the hook.

The most popular tags describing this Horror premade book cover are dark, fantasy, woman, art and portrait.
